    "steam_appid": 1488310,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488310/extras/824e40f0c0bd6d7f9f81a9013dd30b88.avif?t=1758554573\" width=652 height=190 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《名望 Renown》的开放式世界就是你的战场。此地，唯有最强者方可称王。收集资源， 建造宏伟的城堡，率领你的阵营迎战敌对玩家。建造攻城车摧毁敌方城墙，让战场上剑影交错；或与邻国结盟，摧毁敌方阵地——用实力证明自己，赢得属于你的名望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存和探险在充满掠夺的世界里，狩猎、采集、锻造并打造出属于你的要塞。无论是开垦荒山野地、铸造前线武器，还是为氏族建造坚固的防御工事，为了生存，总有任务等着你去完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488310/extras/ab5f9b17212a1403173a5d24bc88ddd5.poster.avif?t=1758554573\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488310/extras/ab5f9b17212a1403173a5d24bc88ddd5.webm?t=1758554573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩张和占领从最不起眼的帐篷，到防御严密的城堡，一切都是你征伐的目标。锁定战略要地，打响战争号角、集结物资；释放攻城车，强势攻下敌方核心堡垒。纵横捭阖抑或者攻城略地，去成为这里的王。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488310/extras/c2f1a131beb0dd1a275207a2e5a7d116.poster.avif?t=1758554573\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488310/extras/c2f1a131beb0dd1a275207a2e5a7d116.webm?t=1758554573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >技术之战胜利靠的是技术而非时运。带上利刃、战锤和盾牌，奔赴生死一战，唯有技艺精湛，方能掌握命运之盘。完美一击和致命错误都可能让战场形势彻底翻转。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488310/extras/98fb4db75f14ff156792bc6a824459f9.poster.avif?t=1758554573\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488310/extras/98fb4db75f14ff156792bc6a824459f9.webm?t=1758554573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独一无二的自定义系统打造你的专属骑士荣光——从盔甲到战袍，从徽章到配色，皆可由你亲手搭配。你可以身披僧袍游走于战场，也可以在血月的旗帜下，与身披红白战甲的勇士并肩作战。一切全由你一念而定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488310/extras/c6819c2009e132c6c50da73fc7deef04.poster.avif?t=1758554573\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488310/extras/c6819c2009e132c6c50da73fc7deef04.webm?t=1758554573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由与无序并存名望的世界是一个缺乏监管的地方，你的决定由你自己做主，而唯一的后果就是来自敌人的报复。随处建造，随意杀戮，掠夺所有人，夺取一切！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488310/extras/1415c155a3307122e84b3a94c9b2dd34.poster.avif?t=1758554573\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488310/extras/1415c155a3307122e84b3a94c9b2dd34.webm?t=1758554573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/b]着重于近战的快节奏中世纪PvP生存体验</p></strong></li><li><strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/b]从建设简单的农场到宏伟的堡垒，一切发展全凭你的掌控</p></strong></li><li><strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/b]团队系统，支持领土宣称、头衔争夺、分配等级等多样玩法</p></strong></li><li><strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/b]从头盔到基地的旗帜，所有细节都可以自定义</p></strong></li><li><strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/b]通过服务器进程和重置系统，为玩家提供沉浸感强、重玩价值高的游戏体验</p></strong></li><li><strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/b]为社区管理者提供工具，助力打造专属环境；未来还计划提供广泛的模组支持</p></strong></li></ul>",
